# Formula Reference Guide
## New Leads Dashboard - Keystone Acquisitions

Quick reference for all formulas used in the dashboard.

---

## KPI Formulas (Section B)

### Total New Leads
```
=COUNTA('Leads Database'!A2:A)
```
Counts all non-empty cells in Lead ID column (starting row 2)

### Leads Received Today
```
=COUNTIFS('Leads Database'!B:B,TODAY())
```
Counts rows where Date Received equals today

### Leads Received This Week
```
=COUNTIFS('Leads Database'!B:B,">="&TODAY()-6,'Leads Database'!B:B,"<="&TODAY())
```
Counts last 7 days including today

### Leads Received This Month
```
=COUNTIFS('Leads Database'!B:B,">="&DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),MONTH(TODAY()),1),'Leads Database'!B:B,"<="&TODAY())
```
Counts from start of current calendar month to today

### Leads Missing Docs
```
=COUNTIF('Leads Database'!S:S,TRUE)
```
Counts all rows where Missing Docs Flag = TRUE

### Leads Awaiting Follow-Up
```
=COUNTIFS('Leads Database'!S:S,TRUE,'Leads Database'!X:X,"<>Completed")
```
Missing docs AND follow-up status is NOT completed

### Leads Flagged for Human Review
```
=COUNTIF('Leads Database'!Y:Y,TRUE)
```
Counts all rows where Human Review Flag = TRUE

### RV Park Leads
```
=COUNTIF('Leads Database'!H:H,"RV Park")
```
Counts all rows where Asset Type = "RV Park"

### Campground Leads
```
=COUNTIF('Leads Database'!H:H,"Campground")
```

### Resort Leads
```
=COUNTIF('Leads Database'!H:H,"Resort")
```

### Seller Financing Mentions
```
=COUNTIF('Leads Database'!U:U,TRUE)
```

### % Missing Docs
```
=IF(A6=0,0,ROUND(E6/A6*100,1))&"%"
```
Percentage with error handling for division by zero

### % Human Review
```
=IF(A6=0,0,ROUND(G6/A6*100,1))&"%"
```

### Leads Added (Last 7 Days)
```
=C6
```
References the "This Week" metric

