## Missing Docs Monitoring Formulas (Section D)

### Total Missing Docs
```
=E6
```
References KPI from section B

### Waiting > 3 Days (no follow-up)
```
=COUNTIFS('Leads Database'!S:S,TRUE,'Leads Database'!B:B,"<"&TODAY()-3,'Leads Database'!X:X,"No Follow-up Sent")
```
Missing Docs = TRUE
AND Date Received > 3 days ago
AND Follow-Up Status = "No Follow-up Sent"

### No Follow-up Sent
```
=COUNTIFS('Leads Database'!S:S,TRUE,'Leads Database'!X:X,"No Follow-up Sent")
```
Missing Docs AND no follow-up sent yet

### Follow-up Sent
```
=COUNTIFS('Leads Database'!S:S,TRUE,'Leads Database'!X:X,"<>No Follow-up Sent",'Leads Database'!X:X,"<>Completed")
```
Missing Docs AND follow-up in progress (sent but not completed)

### Needs Immediate Attention
```
=COUNTIFS('Leads Database'!S:S,TRUE,'Leads Database'!B:B,"<"&TODAY()-3,'Leads Database'!X:X,"No Follow-up Sent")+COUNTIF('Leads Database'!Y:Y,TRUE)
```
Sum of:
1. Missing Docs older than 3 days with no follow-up
2. All leads flagged for human review

