## Helper Formulas

### Last Updated Timestamp
```
=TEXT(NOW(),"MMM DD, YYYY at h:mm AM/PM")
```
Auto-updates whenever sheet recalculates

### Error Handling Wrapper
Most formulas use IFERROR to return "" (blank) instead of error:
```
=IFERROR(formula,"")
```

### Zero Division Safety
KPI percentages use this pattern to avoid errors when totals are zero:
```
=IF(denominator=0,0,calculation)
```

