## Quick Customization

### Change date range for "This Month" to "Last 30 Days"
Replace:
```
DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),MONTH(TODAY()),1)
```
With:
```
TODAY()-30
```

### Change "Waiting > 3 Days" to "Waiting > 5 Days"
Replace:
```
TODAY()-3
```
With:
```
TODAY()-5
```

### Add a new asset type
1. Add to dropdown in Leads Database (Column H)
2. Copy one of the asset type count formulas and change the criteria string
3. Add a new row in Section F with appropriate formulas

### Rename the data source sheet
Use Find & Replace (Ctrl+H):
- Find: `'Leads Database'!`
- Replace with: `'Your New Sheet Name'!`
- Click "Replace All"

